== 考古研究 ==
1968年，在[[河北省|河北省]][[保定专区|保定专区]][[满城县|满城县]]，发掘了埋葬劉勝和王妃竇氏的[[中山靖王墓|中山靖王墓]]。墓中出土[[刘胜金缕玉衣|刘胜金缕玉衣]]以及王妃竇綰的銀縷玉衣。[[刘胜金缕玉衣|刘胜金缕玉衣]]內殘存灰褐色的骨灰和牙齿的[[牙釉質|琺瑯質外殼]]碎片<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://history.people.com.cn/n1/2018/0109/c372327-29754233-2.html |title=揭秘：满城汉墓发掘过程中的惊险和神秘 |accessdate=2019-08-03 |archive-date=2020-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407210606/http://history.people.com.cn/n1/2018/0109/c372327-29754233-2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。竇綰的銀縷玉衣內留有[[脊骨|脊骨]]、[[肋骨|肋骨]]、[[盆骨|盆骨]]以及牙齒的[[牙釉質|琺瑯質外殼]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=fEB7DwAAQBAJ&pg=PT62&lpg=PT62&dq=%E5%88%98%E8%83%9C+%E7%89%99%E9%BD%BF%E7%8F%90%E7%90%85%E5%A4%96%E5%A3%B3&source=bl&ots=IRNuaC-z6t&sig=ACfU3U2phUxoSC4pYepo7wWxY6tgRAApug&hl=zh-CN&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiK4dW3nebjAhXEZt4KHcQ2DzoQ6AEwCnoECAkQAQ#v=onepage&q=%E5%88%98%E8%83%9C%20%E7%89%99%E9%BD%BF%E7%8F%90%E7%90%85%E5%A4%96%E5%A3%B3&f=false |title=古墓探秘 |accessdate=2019-08-03 |archive-date=2020-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200501060206/https://books.google.com/books?id=fEB7DwAAQBAJ&pg=PT62&lpg=PT62&dq=%E5%88%98%E8%83%9C+%E7%89%99%E9%BD%BF%E7%8F%90%E7%90%85%E5%A4%96%E5%A3%B3&source=bl&ots=IRNuaC-z6t&sig=ACfU3U2phUxoSC4pYepo7wWxY6tgRAApug&hl=zh-CN&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiK4dW3nebjAhXEZt4KHcQ2DzoQ6AEwCnoECAkQAQ#v=onepage&q=%E5%88%98%E8%83%9C%20%E7%89%99%E9%BD%BF%E7%8F%90%E7%90%85%E5%A4%96%E5%A3%B3&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。发掘作业中又发现[[长信宫灯|长信宫灯]]、[[漏壺|漏壺]]。

